{"id": 225025252, "title": "Russia now requires Sri Lanka Defence Ministry clearance for ex-servicemen visit visas", "text": "Russia now requires Sri Lanka Defence Ministry clearance for ex-servicemen visit visas Russia will now require clearance from Sri Lanka\u2019s Defence Ministry for visit visas of ex-servicemen, says Sri Lanka\u2019s Minister of Foreign Affairs, Ali Sabry. The Foreign Minister mentioned that he met with the Russian Ambassador in Colombo, Levan S. Dzhagaryan, today (May 29). \u201cWe addressed the urgent situation of Sri Lankans being deployed in the Russia-Ukraine conflict and agreed on immediate steps to resolve these issues,\u201d he said in a post on \u2018X\u2019 (formerly Twitter). \u201cRussia will now require Sri Lanka Defence Ministry clearance for visit visas of ex-servicemen.\u201d He added that the upcoming visit by Sri Lanka\u2019s State Minister of Foreign Affairs, Tharaka Balasuriya, to Russia will allow further discussions to find a solution to this matter.", "summary": "<p>Russia will now require clearance from Sri Lanka\u2019s Defence Ministry for visit visas of ex-servicemen, says Sri Lanka's Minister of Foreign Affairs, Ali Sabry.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.onlanka.com/news/russia-now-requires-sri-lanka-defence-ministry-clearance-for-ex-servicemen-visit-visas.html\">Russia now requires Sri Lanka Defence Ministry clearance for ex-servicemen visit visas</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.onlanka.com\">Sri Lanka News | Breaking News &amp; Top Stories in Sri Lanka | ONLANKA</a>.</p>", "url": "https://www.onlanka.com/news/russia-now-requires-sri-lanka-defence-ministry-clearance-for-ex-servicemen-visit-visas.html", "image": "https://www.onlanka.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/sri-lanka-russia-flags.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-05-29 12:58:06", "author": "Editor", "authors": ["Editor"], "language": "en", "source_country": "lk", "sentiment": -0.352}